    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, curated for the most demanding enthusiast. This vehicle remains in a state of uncompromising preservation, mirroring its original showroom standards in every facet. The exterior finish retains its factory depth and luster, while the interior remains devoid of any discernible wear, reflecting a history of fastidious stewardship. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically peerless, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of true concours-level caliber.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
